item.title: -~-~-~- can anyone tell me how to make a new starting point? -~-~-~-
item.dc:creator: @LittleMaffia LittleMaffia
item.description:
@LittleMaffia wrote:

Search in your player.java for:

 teleportToX

You will see somthing like this :

teleportToX = 3252;//3072; teleportToY = 3435;//3312;

Change the first X and Y coords.

teleportToX = 3252;//3072; teleportToY = 3435;//3312;

Close and save it.

Compile it and you are done!
